**APIHorizonWatch**  
**Description:**  
Continuously monitors API endpoints for trend shifts, response decay, and availability over time.

```markdown
# APIHorizonWatch - Endpoint Trend Scanner

APIHorizonWatch maps API performance across time windows and detects subtle signs of service degradation.

## Features
- Latency curve analysis  
- Status code tracking  
- Export to CSV or JSON

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/APIHorizonWatch.git
cd APIHorizonWatch
python monitor.py
